  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      Aim of this randomized clinical trial is to examine the treatment effectiveness of an
      acupuncture protocol in adult patients with non chronified TMDs.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Therefore there are two treatment arms, acupuncture verum and acupuncture placebo.
      Investigators will evaluate for 4 weeks primary current pain, secondary the unassisted jaw
      opening.
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
